<P>
O.C. EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Admar Group Inc.: The Orange-managed health care services company said its 
third-quarter earnings rose 74% to $47,000 from $27,000 a year earlier. 
</P>
<P>
Revenue for the quarter ended Oct. 31 increased 4% to $2.6 million from $2.5 
million. For the past nine months, earnings nearly doubled to $284,000 from 
$146,000. Revenue increased 3% to $7.7 million from $7.9 million. 
</P>
