<P>
ON THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Columbia Savings and its attorneys have "invented a revolutionary new legal 
strategy -- having a plaintiff plead insanity." 
</P>
<P>
 -- A spokesman for Michael Milken, after Columbia S&amp;L sued Milken on 
grounds that he maniuplated and coerced it into buying more junk bonds than any 
other S&amp;L in America. 
</P>
</TEXT>
